&lt;p&gt;Gap ROIC to WACC = ROIC &amp;ndash; WACC&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Rumus ROIC:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(Laba Bersih+Biaya Bunga)/Invested Capital (Interest Bearing Debt+Ekuitas)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Rumus WACC:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;[ (Interest Bearing Debt)/Invested Capital&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp; Effective Cost of Debt ]+[ Ekuitas/( Invested capital)&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp; Cost of Equity ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Rumus Pendukung:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Effective Cost of Debt = Weighted Average Cost of Debt x (1 - Effective Tax Rate)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Weighted Average Cost of Debt = Biaya Bunga &amp;divide; Interest Bearing Debt&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Effective Tax Rate = Biaya Pajak &amp;divide; Laba sebelum pajak&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cost of Equity = Effective Cost of Debt karena PT Pupuk Indonesia (Persero) menjalankan Public Service Obligation (PSO)&lt;/p&gt;

